RIYADH: Saudi Arabia’s King Salman received a written message from the President of Benin Patrice Talon, the Kingdom’s foreign ministry said on Thursday.
The message was received by Saudi Foreign Minister Prince Faisal bin Farhan, during a meeting with his Beninese counterpart Aurelien Agbenonci at the ministry’s headquarters in Riyadh.
During the meeting, they discussed relations between the two countries and ways to enhance them, in addition to exchanging views on regional and international issues of common interest.